Package: WPD
Title: World Panel Data: A Macroeconomic Data Visualization and Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.0.18
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Peeters", , "benjaminpeeters@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5095-2021"))
Description: A comprehensive panel-data package providing access to global economic 
    and social indicators. The package includes a large database (approximately 50MB) 
    of world panel data that is efficiently loaded on demand through the 'wp_data' 
    function to optimize memory usage. Features include data visualization tools, 
    time series analysis capabilities, and functions for handling seasonal adjustments 
    and trend analysis.
SystemRequirements: At least 100MB disk space for installation.
